<h1>Compare it to Kent's!</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 getaway">
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 200px; background-color: grey;" class="col-md-6 col-xs-8"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6"
    <p>How do the eateries you've visited compare to Kent's Kitchen? It is the opinion of the world renowned food connoisseur Andrew that Kent's has the best PPTâ„¢ of any eatery in Vancouver. </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <blockquote class="pull-right">
      <p>My life has gotten so much better ever since I put Kent's inside me.</p>
      <small><cite title="Josh">Josh</cite></small>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote>
      <p>A revolutionary revolutionizing revolution of groundbreakingness.</p>
      <small><cite title="Chris">My Landlord Larry</cite></small>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote>
      <p>Why would you set the bar so low??</p>
      <small><cite title="Tammam Kbeili">Tam </cite></small>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row col-md-9 pull-left">
    <h2>The Most Talked About Eateries</h2>
    <% @popular_eats.each_slice(4) do |pop_group| %>
      <div class="row">
        <% pop_group.each do |pop| %>
          <div class="well col-md-3">
            <h3><%= pop.name %></h3>
            <small><strong><%= pop.address %></strong></small>
            <p>Reviews: <%= pop.reviews.count %></p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-3 pull-right">
    <h2>Hall of Fame</h2>
    <% @hall_of_fame.each do |hof| %>
      <div class="well">
        <h4><%= link_to hof.name, hof %></h4>
        <small><strong><%= hof.address %></strong></small>
        <p>Score: <%= '%.2f' % hof.total_average %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <hr>
    <h2>Hall of Shame</h2>
    <% @hall_of_shame.each do |hos| %>
      <div class="well">
        <h4><%= link_to hos.name, hos %></h4>
        <small><strong><%= hos.address %></strong></small>
        <p>Score: <%= '%.2f' % hos.total_average %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>

